OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with persistent rain, in
OL,6,Fthe west at first this morning, heavy
OL,7,Fin the northwest. This soon turning to
OL,8,Fthe odd bright spell and showers.
OL,9,FThese wintry over high ground.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FShowers will continue through
OL,12,Fthe evening but will clear slowly from
OL,13,Fthe south overnight. It will become
OL,14,Fcold as clear spells increase.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSaturday:FEarly bright spells, a few
OL,17,Fshowers west. Cloud soon spreads north
OL,18,Fwith rain following. This heavy and
OL,19,Fpersistent with snow to lower levels.
OL,20,FThe wind strengthens to severe gale
OL,21,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
